{"tid":582667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前警務處長曾偉雄獲任九巴和龍運董事 年薪50.4萬元","createTime":"2018-03-06T11:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T11:52:10.000Z","uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bf81891578188170e08434c11435810685ae24","tid":582667,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"載通（0062）宣佈，委任前警務處處長曾偉雄任載通獨立非執行董事和審核及風險管理委員會成員，同時他獲委任為載通兩間附屬公司九龍巴士和龍運巴士董事。委任自昨天生效，年薪50.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n曾偉雄年薪50.4萬元，包括載通獨立非執行董事每年可獲董事袍金32.4萬元，另作為審核及風險管理委員會成員每年將可獲酬金18萬元。曾偉雄2015年5月退任警務處處長，現時在大型注塑機生產商震雄集團（0057）任職策略及管理顧問。<br />\n<br />\n另外，載通同時宣佈數碼通（0315）副主席兼非執董張永銳及新地（0016）公共事務總監李鑾輝為載通非執董及九巴與龍運巴士董事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1514855528101&amp;issue=20180102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1514855528101%26issue%3D20180102&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=3e904fcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1514855528101%26issue%3D20180102&h=5cea1dd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1514855528101&amp;issue=20180102</a>"},{"pid":"f2d1afdcc335c3fd6ec6807fa2f7c2e791836b35","tid":582667,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"佔領九巴"},{"pid":"109bdfdde96ec0ddabe42c64925a57b5a4ab2722","tid":582667,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"以為月薪50萬添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed66c3769f07c9e534b1682a06a9ada47c5caf9b","tid":582667,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109bdfdde96ec0ddabe42c64925a57b5a4ab2722","tid":582667,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"以為月薪50萬添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\